@node "Document_0" "Introduction"

 	Well hello Dude !!

 	So You're running a BBS ??

	And you wanna know if there is a easy way
 	to check youre icoming files ??

	Well here is youre solution to all the problems
 	they'll all be off the past!!
 	Iff you follow these docs carefully then you'll
 	have no problems , but read them carefully !!

	And you'll see when you're finished the BBS will
 	run as smooth as a pussy is slippery :)
@endnode

@node "Document_1" "Installation"

 	There is a Install programm on the disk !!
 	Iff you use it , then there will be no worry's
 	because the things that you have, will be renamed
 	in *.OLD , so nothing will be lost !!

	Ofcourse there will be a part that have to be done
 	manualy, this in sight of the versions you use !!
 	Any programm in the New_Dopus.CFG:C/ directory 	will
        have a version number as comment on the file,
 	check that out and decide then wich of those you
 	wanna replace !!
@endnode

@node "Document_2" "What to do"


 Now there's a bit you have to do manualy, the stuff thats in the
 Dopus dir must be copy'd in the Dopus: on youre HardDisk !!
 In the Dopus dir in the disk is a dir called Checker , you MUST
 assign Checker: to that directory !!
 So This is what have to be in youre user-startup :

            Assign Checker: Dopus:Checker/

 Also there are 2 directory's made in youre S: directory,
 One is called "AutoAdd" in there you must put a Ascii Add of
 youre own !!
 The second dir is called Checkers.DMS.LHA , there are several
 scripts that you have to adapt to youre own needs, specially
 the paths are wrong so configure those to youre own idea !!

@endnode

@node "Document_3" "Additional"

 	Copy the files in New_Dopus.CFG:C/ in youre own C:directory.
 	Copy the Dirs New_Dopus.CFG:Dopus/Arexx &
 	New_Dopus.CFG:Dopus/Checker in youre Dopus: directory.
 	Check to see if the fonts on the disk are already in
 	youre Fonts: directory, if not then do also copy these
 	in the Fonts: directory.

@endnode

